Atrium Outlook Raised to ‘Positive’ From ‘Stable’ at Fitch

-- B y   J o n a t h a n   T i r o n e
-- 
2011-10-18T11:55:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-18/atrium-outlook-raised-to-positive-from-stable-at-fitch.html
Atrium European Real Estate Ltd. (ATRS) ’s
outlook was raised to “positive” from “stable” by Fitch
Ratings today. Atrium’s long-term issuer default rating was
affirmed at “BB+,” Fitch said in a statement.  “Fitch expects Atrium’s financial metrics to remain
resilient and stable int he next two years,” the statement
read.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jonathan Tirone at 
 jtirone@bloomberg.net  